        <h1 class="text-gradient text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text">
          About Us
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Hi there! We’re Sam and Neha, lifelong friends who’ve known each other for 25 years. From classrooms to grad school, we’ve shared almost everything—even becoming roommates!
          <br /><br />
          Like many international students, we struggled with apartment hunting. Over two years, we moved three times, relying on photos and videos that didn’t capture the real vibe of a space. It was frustrating and stressful.
          <br /><br />
          That’s why we created <strong>3D-Ready</strong> and <strong>The Point Cloud</strong>. We wanted a better way to see apartments—clearly and in 3D—so no one has to guess what they’re signing up for.
        </p>
