    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-transparent bg-clip-text text-center">
      Why Choose 3D Models?
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-accent p-6 rounded-lg mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <li><strong>Save space:</strong> 3D models are smaller than photos, making storage and sharing easier.</li>
        <li><strong>Streamlined experience:</strong> No need to manage multiple images and videos of every room.</li>
        <li><strong>Accurate visualization:</strong> See the apartment exactly as it is, with no surprises.</li>
        <li><strong>Save time:</strong> Fewer video calls and in-person tours for landlords and tenants.</li>
        <li><strong>Quick generation:</strong> Easily create 3D models with cutting-edge technology.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-700 text-center">
      With our tech, renting apartments is faster, smarter, and stress-free. Thank you for reading our story!
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-primary text-center">
      Samridha & Neharidha
    </p>
  </section>
